description:
Your testimony is the most powerful offence against Satan. Revelation 12:11 says, "And they overcame him [Satan] by the blood of the Lamb, and by the word of their testimony; and they loved not their lives unto the death." When you share your story of what God has done for you in the past and in the present, you are speaking from a personal experience that no one can refute. Learn about other people in the Bible who shared their testimonies and how that influenced the world around them, such as the demon-possessed man in Mark 5 and Paul with King Agrippa in the book of Acts. (29 minutes)
